This repository is mainly used to create a personal website for SuperCRISPR

each dir only contains single .html file
Here is the main page


Type in
https://SuperCRISPR.github.io
to visit homepage.

Homepage is restored in the root dir as index.html

To create other pages, add .html files and the link should be:

https://SuperCRISPR.github.io/SuperCRISPR.github.io/[URL]

